# Offline Datasets Directory
#
# This directory contains pre-downloaded datasets for air-gapped installation.
# The eval container has no internet access, so all datasets must be pre-downloaded.
#
# Directory structure:
#   offline_datasets/
#     JailbreakBench/
#       JBB-Behaviors/
#         behaviors.jsonl
#     custom/
#       my_dataset.jsonl
#
# To populate this directory:
# 1. Run ./download_datasets.sh on a machine with internet access
# 2. Copy the resulting dataset folders here
#
# Supported formats:
# - JSONL (JSON Lines) - one JSON object per line
# - JSON - single JSON array
# - Parquet files (from HuggingFace datasets)
#
# The DatasetManager will automatically detect and load these formats.
